            <title>[LOG4J2-75] Allow configuration to be setup per webapp. Allow automatic reconfiguration to work properly.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-75</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ContextListener needs to be enhanced to accept a configuration location. Reconfiguration needs to work for a configuration supplied that way.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
